202988062.Title: Premier 20 in. 2.42 cu. ft. Electric Range in Stainless Steel, Silver
202988062.Description: The Premier 20 in. Freestanding Electric Range puts all the features and convenience of a full-size range into a unit that will accommodate even the most intimate of kitchen spaces. All Premier ranges come with an Exclusive Lifetime Warranty on all Top Burner Elements - Your assurance that you are purchasing a top quality product. Equipped with a lift-up cook top and support rod, this range is a cinch to keep clean. Safety features like the Surface Indicator Light, will let you know at a glance if cooktop burners are on. Our "Keep Warm" Thermostat enables you to set your range to 150°, keeping your food warm without continuing to cook until ready to eat and the Fully Insulated Oven comes with 2 Heavy-Duty Oven Racks with 4 Adjustable Positions. Color: Stainless Steel.

316697226.Title: Summit Appliance 20 in. 2.3 cu. ft. Slide-In Electric Range in Stainless Steel, Silver
316697226.Description: Summit's slim-fitting ranges bring true efficiency to smaller kitchens. Model REX2071SSRT1 is a 20 in. wide 220-Volt electric range with a smooth ceramic glass cooking surface complete with 4 1200-Watt elements. Sized just over 24 in. deep, it's ideal for apartments, tiny homes, hotels, and other kitchens with limited space. It ships with a short stainless steel back guard that can be removed to create a more traditional slide-in look. The large oven includes 2 adjustable racks and a waist-high broiler that allows you to switch from bake to broil without moving your dishes. The large oven window and interior light let you monitor your cooking without opening the door to release heat and disrupt the baking process. Upfront push-to-turn controls ensure you won't have to reach over the hot surface to adjust, helping to comply with ADA guidelines for accessibility. Indicator lights on the control panel show when a burner or the oven is on and if the surface is still hot. The stainless steel doors with black accents bring a modern look ideal for any kitchen. This unit is constructed from porcelain and steel for lasting durability. It does not include a power cord but is compatible with standard 40 amp range cords (3 or 4-wire). Additional slim-fitting ranges and matching range hoods are available. Note: this unit does not include a lower storage compartment.

314155350.Title: Summit Appliance 20 in. 2.3 cu. ft. Slide-in Electric Range in Black
314155350.Description: The REX2051BRT is a 220-Volt electric range sized at just under 20 in. wide in a jet black finish. The versatile design includes a removable 2 in. high stainless steel backguard, allowing you the choice of a standard range style or a slide-in look with a flat surface that allows you to better integrate the unit with your own backsplash design. The smooth ceramic glass surface includes four 1200-Watt 6-1/2 in. elements, with a hot surface indicator light for added safety. Inside, the REX2051BRT features a large 2.3 cu. ft. oven made from durable porcelain enamel. The waist-high broiler function is easy to use, with slide-out oven racks that can be adjusted in four different glide positions for the best fit. We include a small two-piece porcelain broiler tray with a grill cover. The large oven window and interior light make it easy to monitor your cooking. With its slim fit, the REX2051BRT is the perfect choice for smaller kitchens with full cooking needs. Additional choices are available in 24 in. wide fits.
